title: Leadbelly's Last Sessions [4 CD] [FLAC]
description:
Leadbelly - legendary singer and songwriter.  Intimate, spellbinding recordings from 1948.  96 songs issued on this 4 disc set, feature the 2 remaining unissued tracks from the Last Sessions, plus his best known songs such as Midnight Special, Goodnight Irene, Rock Island Line and Easy Rider.   

Smithsonian/Folkways.
Copyright 1994.

Ripped from original cd box using EAC to FLAC.
